{
  "verses": [
    {
      "n": 32,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Preeksch firmas Galwas\ntew buhs uszeltees/ un ta Wezza\nWatgu gohdaht/un preeksch tawa\nDeewa bihtees/ Es eſmu tas\nKUNGS."
    },
    {
      "n": 33,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un kad weens Swechi-\nneeks pee tew juhsu Semmê mit-\ntihs/ tad jums ne buhs winnam\ngrehti darriht."
    },
    {
      "n": 34,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tam Swechineekam/kas\npee jums ka Swechineeks mahjo\nbuhs juhsu Starpâ lihds tam\nbuht/ kas tai Semmê dsimmis/\ntew buhs winnu mihtoht/ka ſew\npaschu/jo juhs effat Swechineeki\nbijuschi Egiptes-Semmê/ Es ef-\nmu tas KUNGS juhsu Deews."
    },
    {
      "n": 35,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Jums ne buhs Teefâ ne\nkahdu Netaifnibu darriht ar Oh-\nlekti/Swarru un Mehru."
    },
    {
      "n": 36,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Jums buhs weenn taisnu\nSwarru/ taifnus Pohdus/ un\ntaisnu Puhrnu unStohpu turreht/\nes eſmu tas KUNGS juhsu\nDeews/ kas es juhs no Egiptes-\nSemmes isweddis eſmu."
    },
    {
      "n": 37,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tapehz buhs jums wiſus\nmannus Likkunus/ un wiſas\nmannas Teefas turreht un dar-\nriht/ Es eſmu tas KUNGS."
    },
    {
      "n": �,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ta XX. Nodalla.\nTa Sohdiba tohp teem spreesta/kasjawus Behr-\nnus tam Mohlokam uppure: 2/ 3. Tohs\nSihlneekus un Laika Zeenitajus ne buhs wai-\njaht: 6. Tehwam un Mahtei ne buhs la-\ndeht: 9. Laulibaspahrkahypschann/ Afins\nGrehkus un wiſadu Nescheihstibu buhs par\nnegantu turreht: 10. Deewa Wahrdus\nturreht: 22. Sihlneekus un Laiku Zeenita,\njus buhs nokaut: 27."
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "ntas KUNGSrunna-\njaus Mohsu/ un fazzija:"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tew buhs arri us\nIsraëta Behrneem fazziht: Ik-\nweenam no Israëta Behrneem\nun no teem Swechineekem/ kas\nIsraëta Starpâ miht/ kas no fa-\nwa Dsimmuma tam Mohlokam\ndohd/ tam buhs nokautam tapt/\nteem Laudin tahs Semmes buhs\nwinnu ar Akminneem nomehtaht."
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un es zelschu favu Waigu\nprett to paschu Wihru/ un isdel-\ndefschu to no favu Lauschu Wid-\ndus/tapehz ka tas no favu Dsim-\nmuna tam Mohlokam dewis irr/\nneſchihstu darridams manni\nfwehtn Weetu/ un fagahnidams\nmannu fwehtu Wahrdn."
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un ja tee Laudistanni Sem-\nme tihfchn pehz to ne luhto/ kad\ntas no favu Dsimmuna tam\nMohlokam dohd/ ka tee winnu ne\nnokanj."
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad zelschu es favu Wai-\ngu prett to Wihru/ un prett win-\nxa Saiini/ un isdeldefschu to/ un\nwiſsus/ kas winnam pakkat-\nmaukohs/ pakkatmanfodami\ntam Mohlokam no winna Lau-\nschu Widdus."
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Kad kaslabban pee Siht-\nneekteem/ un Paredsetajeem gree-\nsisees winneem pakkatmauko-\ndans/ prett to paschu zelschu es-\nfavu Waigu/un tsdeldefschu to no\nwinna Lauschu Widdus."
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tapehz fwehtijeetes/ un\neffect fwehti/ jo es eſmu tas\nKUNGS juhsu Deews."
    }
  ],
  "confidence": "high",
  "notes": ""
}
